and we have quite a bit of--

277
00:16:15,344 --> 00:16:17,844
-What the hell happened here?

278
00:16:17,878 --> 00:16:20,044
Di Roy's been killed?

279
00:16:20,078 --> 00:16:22,678
Heh.

280
