took him under his wing,

297
00:17:12,178 --> 00:17:15,978
that Di Roy was never
really much of a warrior.

298
00:17:16,011 --> 00:17:17,678
[growl]

299
00:17:17,711 --> 00:17:20,644
-Whoever for Di Roy
was very fortunate.

300
00:17:20,678 --> 00:17:23,778
Truth is, for an Arrancar,
he was incompetent.

301
00:17:23,811 --> 00:17:27,344
A failure of
unbelievable proportions.

302
00:17:27,378 --> 00:17:29,211
You won't be that lucky.

303
00:17:29,244 --> 00:17:33,378
You're up against me, and I'm
always victorious in battle.

304
00:17:33,411 --> 00:17:36,678
I'll play around until
you're exhausted.

305
00:17:36,711 --> 00:17:38,978
