306
00:17:41,678 --> 00:17:44,944
[maniacal laughter]

307
00:17:44,978 --> 00:17:46,578
[panicked moaning]

308
00:17:50,244 --> 00:17:51,978
-What's happening?

309
00:17:52,011 --> 00:17:53,478
This is so scary.

310
00:17:53,511 --> 00:17:55,111
I hope it's not nearby.

311
00:17:55,144 --> 00:17:56,611
Must be gangs or something.

312
00:17:56,644 --> 00:18:01,778
These guys have no respect,
making such a racket at night.

313
00:18:01,811 --> 00:18:05,011
[groan] My stupid sister.

314
00:18:05,044 --> 00:18:06,311
Seriously.

315
00:18:06,344 --> 00:18:09,111
She should go out and buy
her own damn juice, Oh man.

316
00:18:09,144 --> 00:18:10,278
I hate this area.

317
00:18:10,311 --> 00:18:11,278
It's so dark.

318
00:18:11,311 --> 00:18:12,778
Who knows what's out here?

319
00:18:12,811 --> 00:18:14,111
On top of which,
I've been seeing

320
00:18:14,144 --> 00:18:16,578
